                <!-- display the comment text -->
                <div class='comment_text entry-content-wrapper clearfix'  itemprop="commentText" >
                <p>I prefer the Arduino, made an Android App that controls X10, RF and Infrared using a single Arduino.<br />
It is called X10Domuino on google play , all device status are kept by the Arduino no matter where you control it from.<br />
Using a Raspberry PI it would take a lot more time to develop.</p>
<p>Regards<br />
Philip</p>
